	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's it, I'm switching to asm6. It's simple, compact, easy to use, and has everything you need to assemble a full .nes ROM (with a header, multiple program banks, and all that) in a single step.
<br />
<br />Actually, the only thing I miss are local labels, but I guess the temporary labels will make up for them.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


